4318.title: Dora the Explorer
4318.description: Boots is thrilled to hear about the riddle contest today at the Tall Mountain. Who can solve the silliest riddle?

4319.title: Dora the Explorer
4319.description: Uh oh! A Big Storm Cloud is coming. Dora and Boots have to warn all their friends in the forest to get home fast so the Big Storm Cloud doesn't rain on them and get them wet.

10416.title: Dora the Explorer
10416.description: Boots can't wait for a super duper toy fire truck that's coming in the mail. But when the package arrives, the box is empty! Seems the toy fell out and is now sitting far away on top of Snowy Mountain.

10417.title: Dora the Explorer
10417.description: The stick, the stick, the Magic Stick! Dora and Boots find a magic stick and according to the wise old Tree Frog, it's up to our two young heroes to go to the top of the Highest Hill to make the stick do its magic trick.

16969.title: Dora the Explorer
16969.description: ¡Falta algo! Something's missing! Dora and Boots meet a wizard, El Encantador, who's missing his magic wand! Dora and Boots set off to find El Encantador's wand so he can do his magic.

16970.title: Dora the Explorer
16970.description: Squeaky, squeaky! What's that sound? It's Squeaky, Boots' adorably squeezable new bath toy. But when Boots loses Squeaky, we all have to head to the Gooey Geyser to get him back.

23539.title: Dora the Explorer
23539.description: Meet Rojo, the newest, shiniest red fire truck. Rojo invites our heroes along as he goes on his very first rescue mission - to help a kitten who's stuck in a tree.

23540.title: Dora the Explorer
23540.description: Who do we ask for help when we don't know which way to go? The Map! But today the Map gets mistaken for a stick by a goofy bird. The bird flies Map all the way to his nest on top of Tallest Mountain.

29972.title: Dora the Explorer
29972.description: It's Mother's Day, and Dora wants to help Papi bake Mamá a special cake. But three key ingredients are missing: bananas, nuts and chocolate.

29973.title: Dora the Explorer
29973.description: Go-go-go-golden Explorers! Dora and her friends have formed a soccer team and are playing the big Dinosaurs. Can Dora kick the ball into the net and score a goal?

36700.title: Dora the Explorer
36700.description: Achoo, achoo! What's that sound? Benny the Bull has the sneezes. It's Doctor Dora to the rescue as she sets off to Benny's Barn for a house call.

36701.title: Dora the Explorer
36701.description: Yee haw! Cowgirl Dora and Cowboy Boots are riding through the Wild West on Pinto the Pony Express. They have to deliver a special package of cowboy cookies to Benny the Bull, but they'll have to be on the lookout for Swiper.

43372.title: Dora the Explorer
43372.description: Dora and Boots meet León, a friendly lion who wants to join the circus. They pedal on a unicycle, tightrope walk and skate their way to the Big Top, so León can become a circus lion and do all his tricks.

43373.title: Dora the Explorer
43373.description: Step right up and join the fiesta! Dora and Boots are trying to win the grand prize - the Big Piñata! They need to collect 10 yellow tickets by playing carnival games and rides.

49582.title: Dora the Explorer
49582.description: We all have something that makes us happy, even the Grumpy Old Troll! Dora and Boots set off on a quest to find all the things that make the Grumpy Old Troll happy, so he can do his happy dance.

49583.title: Dora the Explorer
49583.description: Nothing can stop Dora and Boots, they will not fail! Their job is to deliver the mail! Dora and Boots are mail carriers and they need to deliver all the letters, even one to Swiper the Fox!

55828.title: Dora the Explorer
55828.description: Map finds a red cape and becomes super hero for the day. He can jump, he can fly, he can blow clouds away with a single, super breath! He's Super Map! When Dora's mommy calls her home, Dora and Boots need to get home fast.

55829.title: Dora the Explorer
55829.description: Dora has tried and tried, but she's never been able to climb all the way across the monkey bars. Dora and Boots set off for Play Park so Dora can give it another try.

62486.title: Dora the Explorer
62486.description: C'mon and join the musical parade! Dora and Boots are leading a parade over the Piano Bridge and through the Swinging Gate to free the instruments that were locked up by the evil Señor Shhh!

62487.title: Dora the Explorer
62487.description: Dora and her friends are super good at hiding, especially Señor Tucán when he hides in the Rain Forest. If we can find all 8 friends, Señor Tucán promises to introduce us to his new baby toucans.

68981.title: Dora the Explorer
68981.description: Dora and Boots read about a chicken that's as big as a house and set off to meet him.

68982.title: Dora the Explorer
68982.description: Dora and Boots must reunite a baby blue bird with her mother.

75413.title: Dora the Explorer
75413.description: Hic! Boom! Ohhhh!!! What's that funny sound coming from Yellow Valley? Dora and Boots set off to investigate. They'll have to go across the Noisy River, then tiptoe through the Quiet Forest, and that's how they'll get there.

75414.title: Dora the Explorer
75414.description: Dora brings Boots a special present, a new floaty that will help him swim. Boots is thrilled, and they set off for the beach. But first they'll have to go through the Dune maze (watch out for the crabs!), then fix the broken Boardwalk, and that's how they'll get to the beach.

81930.title: Dora the Explorer
81930.description: Deedle dee dee! Dora and Boots hear the ice cream truck nearby, but they just miss it.

81931.title: Dora the Explorer
81931.description: All aboard! It's time for the big train race. First train to the Big Yellow Station wins a big whistle.

88304.title: Dora the Explorer
88304.description: Dora and Boots find a blue key; it turns out it's the key to a big treasure chest.

88305.title: Dora the Explorer
88305.description: Dora and Boots are at the farm today, bringing presents to the three little piggies.

94180.title: Dora the Explorer
94180.description: Boots loses one of his shiny red boots in the Big River. Dora and Boots set off on a wild water adventure as they chase the runaway boot.

94181.title: Dora the Explorer
94181.description: Dora and Boots go hunting for blueberries on Blueberry Hill. But they'll have to be careful--Swiper the fox lives on Blueberry Hill!
